✅ Key Takeaway

This incident was not about a single vulnerable tool — it was about implicit trust in external dependencies combined with non-deterministic builds.

Final Insight:

Unpinned Dependencies
+ Dynamic Resolution (via CI/CD + Trivy workflows)
+ Code Execution on Install
+ High-Privilege AI Environment (LiteLLM)
= Full Supply Chain Compromise Risk

